category: Click Boards > Display & LED > LED Drivers
name: mikroe.click.leddriver9
short_description: LED Driver 9 Click is a compact add-on board that simplifies the control of multiple LEDs. This board features the TLC59116, I2C bus-controlled 16-channel LED driver optimized for red/green/blue/amber (RGBA) color mixing and backlight application from Texas Instruments.
